<T>__{dissolve to:}
<L>__{exterior baker street dawn}
<A>__{the street lamps are still lit. a policeman, on patrol duty, is strolling along the sidewalk, swinging his truncheon. suddenly he sees something up ahead. alarmed, he ducks into the doorway of a building, flattens himself against the door. from the opposite direction comes a horse drawn water sprinkling wagon. the spray covers the sidewalks as well as the street. the policeman waits till the wagon is past, then steps out of the doorway relieved, resumes his patrol.}
